<p>Singing praise to the most locked down device you can get is pretty dangerous for someone operating in the FOSS world. But I have to do it, as the risk of somebody angrily throwing his <a href="https://puri.sm/products/librem-5/">Purism Librem 5</a> at me is pretty low.</p>

