<h1 id="battery">Battery</h1>

<p>Phones have gotten ridiculously big over the years. The iPhone 12 mini doesn‚Äôt feel particularly small. It‚Äôs after you hold any other current phone the size becomes apparent. I still wish it was a little smaller. I really miss the original Palm Pre form factor (and the most stylish OS ever).</p>

<p>People have reported poor battery performance even when the device is relatively new. We‚Äôll see how that‚Äôs going to bite me when we will able to finally travel again, but so far the battery limitation hasn‚Äôt been a constraint for me.</p>

