<p>Even though Apple is probably the corporation most trustworthy of keeping my photos, I‚Äôm still reluctant to have <em>everything</em> synchronized to someone elses computers. Thus the lighting cable and syncing over to a computer is a must. I really wish Apple bit the bullet and discontinued the dinosaur lightning connector in favor of a faster option. But sadly it looks like the successor won‚Äôt be USB3, but no connector at all.</p>

